  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The performance of the ColonRing™ will be comparable to or better than the reported
      performance of staplers.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The proposed study is a post marketing study intended to gather and record additional data to
      further evaluate the performance of the ColonRing™ device in regards to the creation of a
      colorectal anastomosis.

      The study objective is to evaluate the performance of the ColonRing™ in the creation of a
      circular anastomosis in colorectal procedures.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
